        <p>The collection (Donor no. <num type="donor" encodinganalog="541$e">6794</num>) came to the library in June 1982. Originally four feet, the collection included published materials, student records, routine departmental correspondence, duplicates, and some files of Professors Charles David and Kenneth McMurry of minimal informational value. These files have been removed and returned to the donor.</p>
